Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've bonded with a new friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which has allowed you to obtain the Empress Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The disaster looming in your future is claiming human lives as it draws ever closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already possess the power to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you truly need us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the door will open, and we shall offer you our assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2C4CB3&}I'm hot! I'm on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with my melting hot body?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to thrust...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,deeper in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! We actually went inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. This is Yukiko's first time coming here on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't know where Tatsumi Kanji is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can smell that someone's here, but I can't figure out where.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's because I've got so much on my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like where did I come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't seem to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you? Your head's totally empty inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what can we do? Our hands are tied if Teddie can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So like, wanna call it quits this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— Narukami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I could find him if you gave me a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got anything with his scent on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he hasn't been home since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been dangerous out lately, so I notified the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always leaves without saying a word, but this is the first time he hasn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's surprising. I figured he'd usually be out at night fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'll admit he can be a little rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A while ago, he got into a fight with some biker kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean how he beat up an entire biker gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was partially my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep because of their loud bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That made him angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he beat up a biker gang for his mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about an aggressive momma's boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, is that guy in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Um, see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed Sana's cell phone strap with a doll on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I lost the doll and couldn't find it anywhere.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.82,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\t(\blur3)}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&HFF\t(\blur3)}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down! There's no use crying over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make an exact copy, but I could make something like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just apologize when you give it to her and ask for her forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even made one for me to match Sana's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Tatsumi Kanji made that strap from scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It doesn't even look handmade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what to think of Kanji making something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It defies my image of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sana forgave me because of him, so I wanted to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, could I ask you for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His scent should be on it if he made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Didn't we see him yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear? Tatsumi has gone into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, what did you and Kanji talk about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fair enough. I'll tell you upfront since you seem to be in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was ask him about his recent activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It was just small talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I think about it, he was acting a little peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And I bluntly told him as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "You're weird."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That made the color drain from his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's surprising. He doesn't seem like the type to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't judge a book by its cover.
