Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bear acts like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've got Kanji's scent down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to pick up the trail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fail me now, nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniff, sniff! Sniff, sniff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think I found something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like our target! Is this it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
