Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up, Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use your fire spells when it's already this hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too damn hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm freezing. How about a little moderation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see what Hanamura was getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go crazy if we stay here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time he creeps me out, he's toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, what is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi Kanji's a violent delinquent and a bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He trashed a biker gang and became their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks he's "King of the Mountain"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! I never became their boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the one stealing kids' money at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not! Don't assume it was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly Tatsumi Kanji did it. He's that kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make that shit up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out so I can kill ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you put on the scary delinquent act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cut the crap"? You're such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji, the strong and scary delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you want to be seen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're me?!
