Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,He's in here, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Yeah, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Okay, let's go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Yeah, but keep your cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:13:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Yeah, well, no one should lose their temper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,First, we need to rescue Kanji. Then, we gotta save Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Chie, those two objectives were the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Uh, that was intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Huh? It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0095,,Amagi, I seriously don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you opening the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really have to? I bet we're in for an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can just picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What should we do, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is when you guys take the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! I said, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! You're so gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply sublime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— You guys?! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, uh, came...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you sound so unmotivated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsy daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you interfere! Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Is this supposed to slow us down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! It's slimy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami, got a video camera handy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think— Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you drop the charade?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with just saying what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what you really want, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jirai— Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I'll help— Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how I hate girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look at me and say, "You like to sew? What a queer!" or "Painting is so not you."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punk, if you don't shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But you're a man! Why don't act like a guy?! Why aren't you manly?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean to be manly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't scared of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men are much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd never say those awful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I vastly prefer men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you're me, and I'm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't say it, Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way in hell that you're me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're me, and there's no denying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Shadow... The true self...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough shit outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be honest with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll get rid of anyone who gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this is how Kanji truly feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't how he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His emotions are just going haywire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come on, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Teddie! What's the big deal? We've got some real weirdos here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be a part of Kanji's Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a stud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Cha—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could just eat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster! He broke their spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! The guys are down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. They aren't interested in us, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such vulgar red!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't any trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound lovely! It's making my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's time for one last hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,850)}It's time for you to awaken your wild card's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They merged together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike this! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But you're a man! Why don't act like a guy! You aren't you manly?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ecstasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it even though I'm a dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cu—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's super-duper cute! I love anything cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love cutesy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated his own Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it made me happy when you called it cute and accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... He's coming back for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really find him unbearable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't someone, anyone, accept me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, the mere thought that you've been inside me is disgraceful.{gay undertones}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't about men or women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just scared shitless of getting rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a total pansy who tries to make everyone hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're me, and I'm you, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kanji's Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty masculine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, anyone would be surprised out if they found out you made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it! I'm over that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you're being so polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys are my seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, who was the jackass that threw me into the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're trying to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're searching for the culprit? Can I help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta pay him back ten times over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real? That'd be great! You'd be a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Is that okay, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kanji Tatsumi, will risk my life for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi was telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you were hanging out around Tatsumi Textiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.23,0:23:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend took me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't getting into any funny business, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.57,0:23:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're just talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:23:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.57,0:24:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really good!
