Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:04.88,signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\bord8\c&H000000&\pos(446,370)\3c&H08F4E7&\clip(382,374,513,424)\t(715,860,\clip(382,374,513,385))}{LOL "tow" days ago}two
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.74,0:24:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! It's our new early summer release!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, didn't you accept me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.82,0:24:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost something important again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:00.17,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Glaciers of ideas, importing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:01.38,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}To my friends, then exporting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:02.92,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}To the next, keeping it open
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:03.84,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We want no closing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:05.92,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Even without those, our thoughts can be duped
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.43,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}This mind trade no one can stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:09.43,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}An act of thinking is terrible to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:11.14,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We just wanna change it up, not drop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.10,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}And my crew can rock it like uprock{APPARENTLY A REAL THING: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uprock}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:15.06,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Life is tedious if it ain't flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:17.02,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Copy and paste? Constant defaulting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:17.81,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Put my courage to it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:18.65,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Begin showing off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:19.77,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}That's the way we wanna live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:20.69,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Keep going, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:24.07,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}What was so much of transparency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:28.70,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Turned into bright expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:35.45,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Instinct tells me to keep going together, going together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:42.09,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}It's breathtaking moments in life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:49.59,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Addicted to it, minds craving more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:54.35,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}I'm believing you and I can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:58.27,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}We can change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:02.40,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}The sky's the limit, we can spread wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:09.03,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}to roadless travel, together we go
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.86,0:22:21.77,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2}No time to waste
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.77,0:22:22.48,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}but make you pace
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.44,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}It's okay to remove, copy, and paste
Dialogue: 2,0:22:24.44,0:22:25.32,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}I'm doing my way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.32,0:22:26.19,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}You do it your way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:26.19,0:22:27.95,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Don't just follow your left, find the right way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.95,0:22:28.74,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Stereotypes
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.74,0:22:29.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Too many hypes,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:29.66,0:22:31.37,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}But I'm the epitome of new types
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.37,0:22:32.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Having the fear is power to my soul
Dialogue: 2,0:22:32.87,0:22:33.99,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}'Cause I overcome them
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.99,0:22:34.74,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}That's how I roll
Dialogue: 2,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.41,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Expose your thoughts
Dialogue: 2,0:22:36.41,0:22:39.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Don't be afraid of making mistakes
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.87,0:22:42.29,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Rules prevailing in
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.63,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}That may be your greatest rival
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.55,0:22:52.01,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Believe in faith and your heart
Dialogue: 2,0:22:52.01,0:22:56.56,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Your true soul stop being in the shades
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.56,0:23:01.19,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Come on, out in the open sun
Dialogue: 2,0:23:01.77,0:23:06.90,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Beauty of the child of destiny
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.57,0:23:10.57,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Delightful days
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.95,0:23:15.33,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}are with rich density of love
Dialogue: 2,0:23:15.74,0:23:17.12,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Thorny path
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.12,0:23:22.46,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}There's no easy way for real bliss
Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.83,0:23:26.09,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}So I keep on fighting for
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.09,0:23:30.38,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Beauty of destiny
